      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRALEE AIMEE (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 17.63 beating PARK KEY PAW. Well placed and can measure up. AWESOME RETURN (3) was well back throughout but attacked the line strongly to place, 5.5 lengths from the winner (17.73) at this track in Grade 4/5. Won at his only start from this box. Leading chance. SHE'S SILKY (2) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fifth (17.99) at this track last time. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Better than last start and can bounce back. MY BOY MAJESTIC (7) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
